study_inclusion_criteria: All adult patients with cancer diagnosis within 5 years (2016-April 2020) who accepted participation were included since May 2020.
population_group: Patients seeking care for non-COVID-19 reasons

source_name: Seroprevalence study prior and post vaccination in Cancer patients in Principality of Andorra (COVONCO study)
study_inclusion_criteria:
This study included all patients ??? 18 years of age with a
diagnosis of solid tumour or haematological malignancy in the last 5 years (from January 2016-May 2020) who participated in the nation-wide SARS-CoV-2 population screening in May 202015 with means
of serological testing and who provided informed oral consent
study_exclusion_criteria:
Patients who failed to provide informed oral consent, had been cancer-free for the last 5 years or deceased before the start of the study from a
non-COVID-19 related death were excluded. Anonymized use of data was collected as per standard of care.
